title: Throwback Thursday: Juvenile
itunes:title: Throwback Thursday: Juvenile
description:
Today on the show we had to do a throw back Thursday with Juvenile as a special guest! He spoke on his joint album with Birdman, his early days with Cash Money records and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the News team in Toledo Ohio for trying to act young at an old age and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
